[勿助長代購] 自己化妝品自己買！#2<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/257487/page/3?ref=web\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/257487/page/3?ref=web</a><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望連登妝post可以保持返高登幾十個post嘅良好風氣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">問問題前睇清楚#1及懶人包</span></span></strong> <br />\n(e.g. 花水問題及其他熱門產品)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最好Google左先 對想問嘅野有基本了解<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 善用關鍵字搜尋e.g. Google打「xxx lihkg」或「xxx site:<a href=\"http://lihkg.com\" target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com</a>」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講清楚自己要求同基本資料<br />\n（例如：乾性皮膚想搵一隻滋潤光澤型嘅粉底霜，依家用緊XXX 覺得好乾...）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如閱讀後有其他問題可以上POST一齊討論 唔好咁懶豬做伸手黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span> </span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外大家可以留意下animal testing呢樣野, 有好多香港有既品牌都有做動物測試, 例如cdp, dior, shiseido, tom ford, fresh<br />\n想知個brand係咪cruelty-free有幾個方法:<br />\n1)<br />\n如果間公司係中國有實店, 咁佢一定有test on animals, <br />\n因為呢個係中國法律永規定<br />\n2)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.crueltyfreekitty.com/companies-that-test-on-animals/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.crueltyfreekitty.com%2Fcompanies-that-test-on-animals%2F&d=aWL1b99BwFmFs2mBFk4FlvM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=0143f8ca\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.crueltyfreekitty.com/companies-that-test-on-animals/</a><br />\n3)<br />\n<a href=\"http://features.peta.org/cruelty-free-company-search/index.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffeatures.peta.org%2Fcruelty-free-company-search%2Findex.aspx&d=aWL1b99BwFmFs2mBFk4FlvM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=808b9806\" target=\"_blank\">http://features.peta.org/cruelty-free-company-search/index.aspx</a><br />\n4)<br />\nGoogle<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/564x/34/48/b6/3448b68470202f865371d2fe3537c94c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com%2F564x%2F34%2F48%2Fb6%2F3448b68470202f865371d2fe3537c94c.jpg&h=14033483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: violet;\"> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">溫馨提示 </span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為方便爬文 請大家喺加左密既包膠後面加返keywords<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外提大家唔好quote太多圖 記得順便del img code 以免金剛棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1001左果個記得copy返呢度 D 野5分鐘內好開新post啦      <br />\n謝謝大家</blockquote>"},{"pid":"6caaea05549b01fe45dccfda8d14d254d1c35a24","tid":740108,"uid":162373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:06:27.000Z","msg":"唔好俾佢停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"070c6ec51c5e60b654193a9cdcc40f8d06681582","tid":740108,"uid":6018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:38:01.000Z","msg":"真心想知代購d貨點入，好多外國牌子都平專櫃100以上"},{"pid":"e5c51fa5860182b4499d9e579231e311b38c607e","tid":740108,"uid":162373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"070c6ec51c5e60b654193a9cdcc40f8d06681582","tid":740108,"uid":6018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:38:01.000Z","msg":"真心想知代購d貨點入，好多外國牌子都平專櫃100以上"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T03:05:10.000Z","msg":"代購真係要搵朋友買過冇問題既 如果唔係買咗假貨都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj